					<description><![CDATA[I have had major depressive disorder and social anxiety for over 8 years, and I have tried exercising for the past 2 years every other day for at least 30 minutes. I have felt zero effect on my symptoms even combined with therapy. For me I can&#039;t say that exercise has any effect on depression. I wish that wasn&#039;t the case.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have had major depressive disorder and social anxiety for over 8 years, and I have tried exercising for the past 2 years every other day for at least 30 minutes. I have felt zero effect on my symptoms even combined with therapy. For me I can&#8217;t say that exercise has any effect on depression. I wish that wasn&#8217;t the case.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
